==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underditch
<hw>Un`der*ditch"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To dig an
underground ditch or ditches in, so as to drain the surface; to
underdrain; <as>as, to <ex>underditch</ex> a field or a
farm</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underdo</ent>⟦br⟧
